Interface SemanticString

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Identifier, Version
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Base64Binary, HexBinary, IdentifierImpl, IPAddress, IPv4Address, IPv6Address, ISO8601Date, ISO8601DateTime, ISO8601Duration, ISO8601Time, ISO8601TimeZone, PortRange, RFC2396DomainName, RFC822Name, StdVersion, XPathDayTimeDuration, XPathYearMonthDuration

    public interface SemanticString
    SemanticString is an interface for objects that have semantically significant String representations. It differentiates objects whose toString method represents debugging information rather than something that is meaningful at runtime.
